.isodef is the partnew option I just changed the entry text slightly.

When Porteus boots - I follow the Configure steps and select FireFox as the browser, up to the point where it asks to install at 'System Installation' and asks for target device.

Then I click on the 'Browser' button at the bottom of the form to run FireFox.

You can also save the configured ISO to another device. I have not tried this, but presumably you could boot from this saved iso in a similar way and it would not run the Wizard.  

